import React from 'react'
import { Card } from 'react-bootstrap'
import { Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Gallery = () => {
  return (
    <Row>
      <Col md={6}>
        <Card className='my-3 rounded'>
          <Card.Img src={'/Cake/c1.jpg'} variant='top' />
        </Card>
      </Col>
    </Row>
  )
}

export default Gallery
